build SGLang Gemma4 source-stack image	Build and push image	2026-06-12T15:17:44.9355034Z #13 41.56 Python modules in the official Ubuntu repositories are packaged to work with the Python interpreters from the official repositories. Accordingly, they generally won't work with the Python interpreters from this PPA. As an exception, pure-Python modules for Python 3 will work, but any compiled extension modules won't.
